The song Kde kasov m a.m.j for the first time in 1834 on the boards of Stavovské divadlo (the Theatre of the States) in Fidlovačka (Kermesse des sapétiers), the Czech original piece by Josef Kajetán Tyl, accompanied by the music of František Škroup.
It has become popular and people have spontaneously made it appropriate.
