In addition, the bill also mentions meals, and our restaurant has been closed for a long time."
The issuers of zero invoices also did not inquire about the travel agencies in Budapest, which were part of their choice, but only organize travel abroad. Thus, they naively indicated stays in Hungary on invoices to be settled in cash, which also goes against the agency's accounting practices.
They also added VAT on these documents, while travel activities benefits, which are located outside the European Union, are invoiced without VAT.
Similarly, the VAT rate of the four invoices established on behalf of the Hotel Revfülöp in the order of Jobb Jövőért was incorrect, since the company's benefits do not support a 25% VAT as indicated, but a 15% VAT. Furthermore, the hotel employees only issue printed invoices, while the fakes were handwritten.
The prosecution's investigation shows that the "issuers" also made mistakes by mentioning as a provision the carriage of goods by road, that the invoice issuing company could not exercise, since its profile was the investment council.
Moreover, it is also for vices of forms, such as types of inadequate invoices and false stamps, that invoices issued in the order of Együtt a Harmadik Évezredért Alapítvány, of XXI. Századi Kulturális Egyesület and Biztos Pont have proved false.
As in the case of Ravenna Bt. or Kunfehertó's sports internship, which both refuse to be the authors of invoices issued on their behalf.
