Kubatov gave to organizations, 15 invoices in total, issued by Cash Investment, Delta Trió, Fa-Bani Jos, Jos Investment and Linaxtrade, worth HUF 14.2 million.
The public prosecutor's office believed that 10% of the amounts indicated on invoices as well as VAT went to Kubatov's pocket.
Man even used the company Szi-Beri Bt. to establish fictional invoices that were used as part of Biztos Pont's grant application.
